profile:
Cleaning your homes siding, windows, roof, gutters and sidewalks doesn’t have to be a mammoth task. Canadian Pro Clean’s got your back! With a little bit of care and specialized equipment, we’ll have your home looking like new in no time.

Located in Chilliwack and serving the Fraser Valley, Canadian Pro Clean specializes in those sometimes difficult and often overlooked home cleaning and maintenance tasks that raise curb appeal and revitalize the exterior of your home. Our process is designed to safely clean any surface in a way that doesn’t harm the environment and lasts longer than other methods.

From start to finish, you can expect a seamless process. From our customer service to complimentary consultation, exceptional service standards and relentless dedication to satisfaction, you're part of our Pro Clean Family and we will always appreciate each and every customer.
